---
By: Dalai Lama
Source:
  URL: https://twitter.com/DalaiLama/status/997409019856699392
  Locus:
    Date: 18 May 2018
---
People inflict pain on others in their selfish pursuit of happiness and
satisfaction, Yet true happiness comes from a sense of brotherhood and
sisterhood, We need to cultivate a sense of universal responsibility for
one another and the planet we share.
